==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Universally
<hw>U`ni*ver"sal*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a universal manner;
without exception; <as>as, God's laws are <ex>universally</ex> binding
on his creatures</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Universalness</ent>⟦br⟧
